<h1>Analysis of <i><%= @name %></i></h1>

<p>⚡⚡⚡ Energy like <%= @analysis.energy[0] %> (<%= (@analysis.danceability[1] * 100).to_i %>% energy) ⚡⚡⚡</p>

<p>💃💃💃 Danceable as <%= @analysis.danceability[0] %> (<%= (@analysis.danceability[1] * 100).to_i %>% danceability) 💃💃💃</p>

<p>😊😟😐 Feels like <%= @analysis.valence[0] %> (<%= (@analysis.valence[1] * 100).to_i %>% positivity) 😐😟😊</p>

<h3>Standout Tracks</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Oozing with joy: <%= describe_track(@analysis.highest_valence) %></li>
	<li>Sordid and depressing: <%= describe_track(@analysis.lowest_valence) %></li>
	<li>Brimming with excitement: <%= describe_track(@analysis.highest_energy) %></li>
	<li>Nap time: <%= describe_track(@analysis.lowest_energy) %></li>
	<li>Boogie down with: <%= describe_track(@analysis.highest_danceability) %></li>
	<li>Slowing things down: <%= describe_track(@analysis.lowest_danceability) %></li>
</ul>

<h3>Track Count by Year of Release</h3>

<%= bar_chart @analysis.release_date_range,
	id: "yearly-chart",
	width: "800px", height: "#{100 + 18 * @analysis.release_date_range.size}px",
	xtitle: "Count", ytitle: "Year", round: 0,
	discrete: true
%>

<p><%= link_to '<< Back', action: 'show' %></p>